hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: In tens, please (ten pound notes) vida pharmacy You give the Tea Party far too much credit. They are incapable of thinking as deeply as you suggest; they are delusional and simplistic. They are in denial, disconnected from reality. They are anti-government while being wholly dependent on government. They have no idea how things work (“get your government hands off my medicare” is not just an anecdote, but a typical example of their level of understanding).
